# How Many Drops of Essential Oil in an Ounce?

Welcome! I’m Elizabeth Ashley—UK Director for the National Association for Holistic Aromatherapy (NAHA), author of *The Secret Healer Aromatherapy Manuals*, and a practicing clinical aromatherapist with over 30 years of experience.

In this quick, practical tutorial I answer a question every beginner asks:
**“How many drops of essential oil should I use in an ounce of carrier oil?”**

This guide follows classical aromatherapy training, using the **standard reference of 20 drops per millilitre (ml)** to make dilution maths simple for home use.

