## 📝 What You’ll Learn in This Video

✅ **20 drops per ml rule** explained in easy terms  
✅ **How to calculate total drops per ounce (600 drops)**  
✅ **Dilution percentages made simple** (1%, 2%, 3%, 5%)  
✅ **How to blend essential oils safely** for massage, face, bath, or therapeutic use  
✅ When to **adjust your dilution** for sensitive skin, children, or targeted relief

This video will help you confidently calculate blends whether you’re making a teaspoon, ounce, or bottle of essential oil preparation.

